                    <span>I read the older edition 'The Healing of America'. I agreed with what Ms. Williamson said in the book about what is good and bad about America. My only complaint is it came across as a rant at times. It's the reason I gave it four stars instead of five. Still, the book is worth owning because it has lots of practical information in the back.</span>
                  
